SharpNEAT, a C# .Net implementation of NEAT now has a rudamentary web 
site where you can download the current source code and .Net binaries.  
There is also a brief set of questions and answers that explain what 
it's all about and where it's going. There are no pretty graphs or 
pictures as of yet,  following discussions on the group this area is 
next on my list of things to do :)

http://www.cgreen.dsl.pipex.com/
